data.description: Perfect for entertaining!  You will not believe how much living space and functional storage there is in this well maintained split level in the desirable Spring Ford School District. The recently finished and completely enclosed sunroom (2022) offers a serene space for your own personal oasis that combines outdoor ambiance with indoor comfort. Outside you will find an inground pool complete with pool shed, in addition to two other sheds on this .86 acre property. The basement offers a bonus flexible space with many options to fit your individual needs. So many major updates are already completed for peace of mind including a kitchen renovation (2020) pool liner and resurfacing (2022) central AC (2022) conversion to gas heat (2021) new hot water heater (2021) outdoor drainage system (2021) and more. Convenient location to major roadways and shopping with easy access to downtown Phoenixville, Oaks Expo Center, King of Prussia and Providence Town Center.
